1
00:00:01,220 --> 00:00:03,584
A storm is approaching the city.

2
00:00:03,653 --> 00:00:08,305
 It will destroy the Force Domes and give us a second chance.

3
00:00:08,405 --> 00:00:11,464
But this is an unnatural tempest,

4
00:00:11,935 --> 00:00:18,903
born in the forbidden mountains where a sinister presence 
tainted the forest a long, long time ago.

5
00:00:19,692 --> 00:00:23,293
A mythical figure they called the Deathless.

6
00:00:23,492 --> 00:00:28,626
The more I discover about this land, the more secrets keep cropping up.

7
00:00:28,830 --> 00:00:32,163
I’m afraid that I have unleashed a terrible power.

8
00:00:32,197 --> 00:00:36,136
And now I’m going to let it blast through this tormented city.

9
00:00:36,757 --> 00:00:40,138
Hopefully it was worth it.

